sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as "调用方"
    participant SM as "状态机 (Continuation)"
    participant Dispatcher as "Dispatcher"
    participant Thread as "工作线程"
    
    Caller->>SM: 调用 suspend fun (label=0)
    SM->>SM: fetchToken(sm) — 传入自身作为续体
    SM-->>Caller: 返回 COROUTINE_SUSPENDED
    Note over Caller: 调用方线程被释放<br/>可执行其他协程

    Thread->>SM: token 就绪, 调用 resumeWith(token)
    SM->>Dispatcher: dispatch(continuation)
    Dispatcher->>Thread: 调度到目标线程
    Thread->>SM: invokeSuspend(token) — label=1
    SM->>SM: fetchData(token, sm)
    SM-->>Thread: 返回 COROUTINE_SUSPENDED
    Note over Thread: 线程再次被释放

    Thread->>SM: data 就绪, 调用 resumeWith(data)
    SM->>Dispatcher: dispatch(continuation)
    Dispatcher->>Thread: 调度到目标线程
    Thread->>SM: invokeSuspend(data) — label=2
    SM-->>Caller: 返回最终结果 "Result: data"
